snippet.title: Hogwarts Legacy - Nintendo Switch 2 Trailer | Nintendo Direct
snippet.description:
Hogwarts Legacy is coming to Nintendo Switch 2 on the day the new Switch console launches on June 5, 2025. Get a quick look at some Hogwarts Legacy gameplay in this trailer.

#IGN #NintendoSwitch2
